extendedInfo.description: -3 Free trials.-Over 5000 SAT Words (in full version)-Has all words with letters starting from a through g-Includes High Frequency Word List-Save options to save your own word lists-View words alphabetically or in random order-Hide definition or word to quiz yourself-**New Feature**-Word of the Day Widget-**New Feature**-Quiz mode
